<section>
  <p>Hey 👋 It’s DJ Sprenk!</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Background & Expertise</h2>
  <p>
    DJ Sprenk is a Brazilian Zouk DJ based out of Cambridge, MA, USA, known for musicality and energetic flow. With a
    background in performing and arranging music, their approach to DJing is deeply rooted in music theory and emotional
    storytelling.
  </p>
</section>

