<section>
  <h2>DJ Journey</h2>
  <p>
    Starting out in the social dance world through Ballroom, Salsa, Bachata, and Kizomba before discovering Brazilian
    Zouk, DJ Sprenk made their DJ debut in 2021 in Boston, MA. By 2022, bookings increased significantly, and by 2024
    the Mixcloud channel had reached over 3 million minutes of listening time with 1,000+ followers and 100,000+
    listens.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Teaching Focus</h2>
  <p>
    Beyond performing, DJ Sprenk is passionate about education — breaking down the craft of Zouk DJing to help others
    develop their ear, improve transitions, and understand energy management on the dance floor.
  </p>
  <p>Personal interests include technology, design, storytelling, and education.</p>
</section>
